{# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   STORY: Why we exist
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<section class="about-story">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-story__layout">
      <div class="about-story__content">
        <span class="about-story__label">The Problem</span>
        <h2 class="about-story__title">Why We Started Vouch</h2>

        <div class="about-story__text">
          <p>
            The wireless industry has been broken for years. Major carriers prioritize profits over people,
            using <strong>complex pricing</strong>, <strong>hidden fees</strong>, <strong>credit checks</strong>,
            and <strong>long-term contracts</strong> as barriers to service.
          </p>
          <p>
            Millions of Americans struggle to get connected—not because they can't afford service,
            but because the system wasn't designed for them.
          </p>
          <p>
            We saw an opportunity to do things differently. By partnering with AT&T's network,
            we deliver the same premium coverage without the premium barriers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-story__quote">
          <blockquote>
            "Vouch Mobile is for everyone who deserves honest, affordable wireless service—no exceptions."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-story__visual">
        <div class="about-story__card about-story__card--problem">
          <div class="about-story__card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>The Old Way</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Credit checks required</li>
            <li>2-year contracts</li>
            <li>Hidden fees & taxes</li>
            <li>Complex plan structures</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="about-story__card about-story__card--solution">
          <div class="about-story__card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>The Vouch Way</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>No credit check ever</li>
            <li>Cancel anytime free</li>
            <li>All-inclusive pricing</li>
            <li>Two simple plans</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

